Signature of Sponsor
AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1881 House Bill No. 1640*
by adding the following new subdivision (vi) in SECTION 1(a)(2)(D):
(vi) Notwithstanding this subdivision (a)(2)(D), the office of homeland security shall
provide any information, record, or other documentation to a member of the general assembly
upon request, including information, records, and documentation relating to critical
infrastructure. A member who receives such information, records, or documentation shall
maintain such information, records, or documentation confidentially.
